#hero
  .container
    .row
      #hero-tagline
        .span7
          %h1 
            Bring patients from the web to your waiting room.
          = link_to "Learn More", about_url, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large"
        .span5
          = image_tag("http://placehold.it/380x292")
.container
  #hero-description
    .row
      .span12
        %p
          Hospitals and health systems need a steady stream of content to engage patients
          online. CareContent licenses a repository of customizable web content - health feature stories, patient quizzes,
          illustrations, current medical news articles, and more. Now, hospitals can efficiently publish patient e-newsletters,
          update landings pages and drive traffic from social media to their websites. Just select your content, add quotes from 
          your own clinicians, along with information about your organization's services and accolades. Then, publish.
  #hero-content
    .row 
      .span12
        %h3.hero
          CareContent covers what current and prospective patients are looking for online:
      .span3
        = image_tag("jobs-careers.jpg")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "Jobs and Careers", "#"
          %p
            Leverage traffic to one of your most visited landing pages. Give job search tips, while directing job seekers to your organization's services.
      .span3
        = image_tag("general-health.jpg")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "General Health/Medicine", "#"
          %p
            Keep patients engaged with new insights on medical care and staying healthy - all with your hospital's unique perspective. 
      .span3
        = image_tag("ortho.jpg")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "Orthopedics", "#"
          %p
            Discuss how your services can find the source of pain, restore impaired mobility and get patients back to living an active life. 
      .span3
        = image_tag("cancer-care.jpg")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "Cancer Care and Survivorship", "#"
          %p
            Tap into the challenges and triumphs of cancer care with content that answers questions, calms doubts, and lets patients know you're with them all the way.
    .row
      .span3
        = image_tag("cardiology.jpg", :width => "220px", :height => "145px")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "Cardiology Services", "#"
          %p
            When patients come to you about matters of the heart, keep them engaged by helping them understand their condition and how you can manage it together. 
      .span3
        = image_tag("obsterics.jpg")
        .hero-categories
          %h3
            = link_to "Obstetrics", "#"
          %p
            Expectant mothers come to you for one reason - to make sure everything is okay. Keep reassuring her or answering her questions, even when she's not there. 
